Signalkeeper is a prototype AI assistant designed to support Account Executives with fast, contextual feedback on active deals.

It evaluates sales conversations, email threads, and transcripts to provide high-level insights, strategic suggestions, and early warning signs of risk or disengagement. Signalkeeper isnâ€™t just a chatbotâ€”itâ€™s a judgment engine, tuned to the nuances of deal health, intent, and emotional tone.

